{"title": "Herbert West: Reanimator", "description": "\"Herbert West\u2014Reanimator\" is a story by American horror fiction writer H. P. Lovecraft that was first serialized in February through July 1922 in the amateur publication Home Brew. The story was the basis of the 1985 horror film Re-Animator and its sequels, in addition to numerous other adaptations in various media. You want zombies? Listen to this because Lovecraft was one of the very first and he got zombies right: scary, evil, implacable and out to get you. (Summary by Phil Chenevert)", "duration": 5378, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "424", "name": "H. P. Lovecraft"}], "coverArt": "http://archive.org/download/LibrivoxCdCoverArt32/herbert_west_1306.jpg", "copyright_year": "0", "genres": ["Science Fiction"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "Phil Chenevert"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Phil Chenevert"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Phil Chenevert"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "Britannia"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "1 - From the Dark", "readers": [5717], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/herbertwest_reanimator_pc_librivox/herbertwestreanimator_1_lovecraft_64kb.mp3", "duration": 916}, {"section": 2, "title": "2 - The Plague-Daemon", "readers": [5717], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/herbertwest_reanimator_pc_librivox/herbertwestreanimator_2_lovecraft_64kb.mp3", "duration": 889}, {"section": 3, "title": "3 - Six Shots by Moonlight", "readers": [5717], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/herbertwest_reanimator_pc_librivox/herbertwestreanimator_3_lovecraft_64kb.mp3", "duration": 871}, {"section": 4, "title": "4 - The Scream of the Dead", "readers": [5717], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/herbertwest_reanimator_pc_librivox/herbertwestreanimator_4_lovecraft_64kb.mp3", "duration": 859}, {"section": 5, "title": "5 - The Horror From the Shadows", "readers": [5717], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/herbertwest_reanim